The fit found the minimum of the negative log-likelihood function for the parameter values shown in Table 3. The estimators for the nuisance parameters, which parameterise their optimal shift relative to the default value 0 in terms of their uncertainty, are found to be δ^=0.62±\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
